title: 2013-14 patch (v1.3) for FIFA 11
description:
2013-14 patch (v1.3) for FIFA 11

included:
- FIFA 11 Selector:
* improvements & fixes

- Squads
* updated player stats, team formations & tactics (from EA official update 26-07-2014)
* 2014 Summer Transfers (14-08-2014)
most of the transfers of russian, english, italian (serie a), german (bundesliga 1), spanish (liga 1), french (ligue 1)
(+ some of other leagues, ...)
* New players like: Halilovic (barca b), Tielemans (rsc anderlecht), ...
* national teams: World cup formations/selections

Installation:
1. install fifa 11 
2. install ea patch (1.01)
3. install 2013-14 patch (v1.1)

4. install 2013-14 patch (v1.3)
* 1_2013-14 patch (v1.3) for FIFA 11.exe
* 2_2013-14 patch (v1.3) for FIFA 11_Missing minis.exe (--> forgot to include these files in first installer)

- patch v1.1 NEEDED, later patches are included
